Sarek Paper

Plot Giab and HCC1395 validation results

Friederike Hanssen

April 21, 2023

QBiC

1 Introduction

For germline benchmarking the datatsets HG002-HG004 were run through the pipeline by combining each mapper with all variant callers. For somatic benchmarking a dataset from the HCC1395 cell line was run through the pipeline by combining each mapper with all variant callers.
